Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.29,0:00:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，道人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.89,0:00:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.79,0:00:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊的天氣如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊還是每天都在下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.87,0:00:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那次分開已經一個月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我今天和大家一起去買東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.31,0:00:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果看到一件有趣的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至從道人先生離開城市之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人每天都利用網路通訊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.58,0:00:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了減少不能見面的寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.55,0:00:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直談著一些日常生活趣事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.49,0:00:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，咦，怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.93,0:00:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼表情突然很驚訝的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要低頭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.93,0:00:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，浴巾，浴巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.44,0:01:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哇！?\N- 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該早點告訴我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.54,0:01:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，道人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.65,0:01:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.58,0:01:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦，通訊中斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.32,0:01:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道人先生，道人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.62,0:01:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實這種事情也是很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…這次的通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.36,0:01:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最後一次的通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.53,0:01:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(ANGEL HEART)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，飯已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.88,0:01:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.29,0:01:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得…現在不要管她比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.86,0:02:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳們不覺得道人太無情了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經兩個星期沒有連絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.07,0:02:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道距離越遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會讓人越來越疏遠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.37,0:02:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖然是這樣講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.84,0:02:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要甩至少也要講出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不出聲實在太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.04,0:02:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果道人先生和久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.85,0:02:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是抱著玩的心情的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會原諒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道人先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.80,0:02:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，耶雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.81,0:02:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個地址…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神維道人…就是指那個道人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.95,0:02:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，道人先生的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.22,0:02:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼耶雪麗亞會知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美一直不願意告訴別人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳又去偷竊別人的機密了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.69,0:03:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶雪麗亞，妳怎麼可以偷看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很瞭解沙希的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.43,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不試試看不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要直接去問道人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不和久留美連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.10,0:03:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶雪麗亞不是正打算這麼做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.24,0:03:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.58,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很早以前就知道會有這樣結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.05,0:03:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果讓久留美知道原因的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會比現在更加失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才沒有講出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶雪麗亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底知道些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.83,0:03:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道人先生的ID號碼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.98,0:04:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ID？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.25,0:04:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,號碼E32459-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個很普通的號碼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,減…這是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無免疫者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無免疫者…是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人類無法生存的惡劣環境下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強迫繼續生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果身心承受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識下將自己生命給停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體能力衰退症候群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無免疫者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個減號就是發病者的記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說道人是…無免疫者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.69,0:04:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說連自己不想活的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說喜歡久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣久留美會變成怎樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要死就自己去死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.34,0:04:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡玲加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個病就算自己多想繼續活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是身體卻自己走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體自己走向死亡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.41,0:05:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，我們是在這城市裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉強的存活了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本應該死的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說身為生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而失去平衡的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連生命的活動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都開始消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶雪麗亞，妳認為道人他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還在考慮要不要去證實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，也許…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相相愛著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要繼續活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法繼續活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.43,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我一直沒有告訴妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳知道這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才對久留美的戀情不太樂觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.37,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們活在這種世界呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一日都會滅亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想和自己所愛的人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是多麼的絕望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.22,0:06:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕不可能獨自生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是個無免疫者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.79,0:06:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我唯一可以活下去的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.13,0:06:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是久留美，沙希，卡玲加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因為遇見妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我有著活下去的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想留在最喜愛的人身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有最純真的友誼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才可以繼續活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳們讓我瞭解了這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以久留美一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以呼喚天使的久留美一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.09,0:07:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許可以停止道人的病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是這樣的想著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶雪麗亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.14,0:07:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許那只是物理現象的發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很想相信奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就和我的時候一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是很卑鄙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.08,0:07:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想久留美一定會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.62,0:07:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.69,0:07:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，我最喜歡妳們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發信地址呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.74,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫院就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.88,0:07:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是道人先生嗎，我是久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你完全沒有音訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我非常擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道人先生，我為了要去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始打工存錢買車票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快存夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為外出日只有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能當日來回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還是很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那時候…見面的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吻我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我最愛的就是道人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望你親我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.21,0:08:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像講了一些很不好意思的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為好不容易才能見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會興奮的把話給講出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道人先生，你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情為什麼那麼痛苦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們好不容易才見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.91,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才見面的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.89,0:09:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經知道了嗎…久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣，妳還…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以呼喚天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為愛上你之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.23,0:09:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使就出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就到道人先生的身邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.44,0:09:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為天使可以讓道人得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，道人現在很痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以呼喚天使！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.19,0:09:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…拜託你…不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.92,0:09:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.73,0:10:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當人與人接觸所產生的奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.16,0:10:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那正如凌小路博士所設計出一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣命名著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGEL LIZENT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使的降臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.61,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喚出那天使的處女心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將那思戀封印起來的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稱為…ANGEL HEART
